modName: BD UUNP Armor replacer high heel boot remover
summary: This is a replacement of some high heel boots of BD UUNP Armor replacer which you do not have option or set by default in bodyslide.
descriptionHtml:
This mod requires [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89849]BD UUNP Armor replacer[/url]﻿ version 1.6
The meshes are from [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72397/]Sexy Vanilla Female Armor Bodyslide UUNP CBBE 7Base MCBM UNP(B) HDT[/url]﻿

If you use racemenu or enhanced character edit changed your character scale, BD UUNP Armor replacer's high heel will reset your character height. Because the high heels were hdt high heels stuffs.
If you think the high heels are unnecessary, and the bugs are annoying, you can use this mod to replace them.

How to use it: 1- override files
2- run bodyslide batch build
author: yhniiii
